    "Adjustments for age and multiple pregnancies were made using multiple logistic regression and we found no statistically significant difference among the three groups.",
    "Conclusion: Patients with PCO±PCOS do not have more adverse obstetric outcomes when compared with non-PCO patients undergoing IVF treatment.",
